entries.s_43: Agent Waray reporting in. I have been unable to infiltrate the bunker, and therefore unable to hinder the Chirq Council's research into biological weapons. I request your assistance. Please invade this bunker, retrieve whatever data you can find on their biological weapon capabilities, and take down some of their chemists.
entries.s_44: You shouldn't salute me, but I'll help.
entries.s_47: Of course. I shall complete my assignment on my own. Very good.
entries.s_48: My assignment is now complete. I'll make certain that my report includes a complete and accurate account of your generous assistance on my behalf.
entries.s_49: As per our previous discussion, please invade this bunker, retrieve whatever data you can find on their biological weapon capabilities, and take down some of their chemists.
